Modifications Copyright (c) 2026, Saman Seifi (Boston University)

This fork includes the following modifications to the original Tahoe 2.1 source:
  - Replacement of the legacy Makefile build system with CMake
  - C++11 two-phase template name lookup fixes across toolbox headers
  - Compiler warning cleanup (-Wwrite-strings, -Wformat, -Wformat-overflow,
    -Wformat-extra-args, C++-only flags guarded from C compilation units)
  - Replacement of #pragma message directives with standard comments

These modifications are distributed under the same BSD 3-Clause license terms
as the original work above.

